<lb n="0450c07"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0450c08"/>
<lb n="0450c09"/><head type="no">No. 724</head>
<lb n="0450c10"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title>佛說罪業<note n="0450007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">應報＝報應【明】＊</note><app n="0450007"><lem>應報</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">報應</rdg></app>教化地獄經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0450c11"/>
<lb n="0450c12"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0450008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔後漢…譯〕十字－【元】</note><app n="0450008" word-count="10"><lem>後漢<note n="0450009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔安息三藏〕－【宋】【宮】，安息＋（國）【明】</note><app n="0450009"><lem>安息三藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">安息國三藏</rdg></app>安世高譯</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0450c13"/><div1 type="jing"><p>如是我聞。一時佛住王舍城耆闍崛山中。與
<lb n="0450c14"/><note n="0450010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0450010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔大〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0450010"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>菩薩摩訶薩及聲聞眷屬俱。亦與比丘比
<lb n="0450c15"/>丘尼優婆塞優婆夷及諸天龍鬼神等。皆悉
<lb n="0450c16"/>集會。爾時信相菩薩白佛言。<note n="0450011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔世尊〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0450011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔世尊〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0450011"><lem>世尊</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。今有地
<lb n="0450c17"/>獄餓鬼畜生奴婢。貧富貴賤種類若干。唯願
<lb n="0450c18"/>世尊。具演說法。若有眾生聞佛說法。如孩子
<lb n="0450c19"/>得母。如病得醫。如<note n="0450012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羸得食＝裸得衣【三】【宮】</note><note n="0450012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">羸得食＝裸得衣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0450012"><lem>羸得食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">裸得衣</rdg></app>。如暗得燈。世尊
<lb n="0450c20"/>說法利益眾生亦復如是</p>
<lb n="0450c21"/><p>爾時世尊觀時已至。見斯菩薩勸請慇懃。即
<lb n="0450c22"/>放眉間白毫相光照于世界。地獄休息苦痛
<lb n="0450c23"/>安寧。爾時一切受罪眾生。尋佛光明來詣佛
<lb n="0450c24"/>所。遶佛七匝為佛作禮。勸請世尊。敷演道化
<lb n="0450c25"/>令此眾生得蒙解脫</p>
<lb n="0450c26"/><p>爾時信相菩薩為諸眾生。而作發起。前白佛
<lb n="0450c27"/>言。世尊。今有受罪眾生。為諸獄卒剉碓斬身。
<lb n="0450c28"/>從<note n="0450013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">頭至足＝足斬之【三】【宮】</note><note n="0450013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頭至足＝足斬之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0450013"><lem>頭至足</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">足斬之</rdg></app>。乃至其頂斬之已訖。<note n="0450014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">巧＝旋【三】【宮】</note><note n="0450014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">巧＝旋【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0450014"><lem>巧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">旋</rdg></app>風吹活
<lb n="0450c29"/>而復斬之。何罪所致。佛言。以前<note n="0450015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世＝身【三】【宮】</note><note n="0450015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世＝身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0450015"><lem>世</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">身</rdg></app>時<note n="0450016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坐＋（齋日殺生）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0450016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">坐＋（齋日殺生）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0450016"><lem>坐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">坐齋日殺生</rdg></app>不
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0724.0451a" n="0451a"/>
<lb n="0451a01"/>信三尊不孝父母。屠兒魁膾斬截眾生。故獲
<lb n="0451a02"/>斯罪。第二復有眾生。身體頑痺眉鬚墮落舉
<lb n="0451a03"/>身洪爛。鳥栖鹿宿人跡永絕。<note n="0451001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沾＝砧【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沾＝砧【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451001"><lem>沾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">砧</rdg></app>污親族人不
<lb n="0451a04"/>喜見。名<note n="0451002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＝為【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之＝為【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451002"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">為</rdg></app>癩病。何罪所致。佛言。以前世時
<lb n="0451a05"/>坐不信三尊。不孝父母破壞塔寺。剝脫道
<lb n="0451a06"/>人<note n="0451003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斬＝斫【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斬＝斫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451003"><lem>斬</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">斫</rdg></app>射賢聖。傷害師長常無返復。背恩忘
<lb n="0451a07"/>義。常行苟且。婬匿<note n="0451004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尊卑無所忌諱＝所尊不避親&CB00565;無有羞恥【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尊卑無所忌諱＝所尊不避親&CB00565;無有羞恥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451004"><lem>尊卑無所忌諱</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">所尊不避親&CB00565;無有羞恥</rdg></app>。故獲斯
<lb n="0451a08"/>罪</p>
<lb n="0451a09"/><p>第三復有眾生。身體長大聾騃無足宛轉腹
<lb n="0451a10"/>行。唯食泥土以自活命。為諸小蟲之所唼食。
<lb n="0451a11"/>常受此苦不可堪處。何罪所致。佛言。以前世
<lb n="0451a12"/>時坐為人自用不信好言善語不孝父母反戾
<lb n="0451a13"/>時君。<note n="0451005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＝若【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">或＝若【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451005"><lem>或</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">若</rdg></app>為帝<note n="0451006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">主＝王【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">主＝王【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451006"><lem>主</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">王</rdg></app>大臣四鎮方伯州郡令長
<lb n="0451a14"/><note n="0451007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吏＝里【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吏＝里【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451007"><lem>吏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">里</rdg></app>禁督護。恃其威勢侵奪民物。無有道理使
<lb n="0451a15"/>民苦悴<note n="0451008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吁＝呼【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吁＝呼【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451008"><lem>吁</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">呼</rdg></app>嗟而行。故獲斯罪</p>
<lb n="0451a16"/><p>第四復有眾生。兩目盲瞎都無所見。或抵樹
<lb n="0451a17"/>木或<note n="0451009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">墮＝陷【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">墮＝陷【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451009"><lem>墮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">陷</rdg></app>溝坑。於時死已更復受身。亦復如
<lb n="0451a18"/>是。何罪所致。佛言。以前世時坐不信罪福障
<lb n="0451a19"/>佛光明。縫鷹眼合籠繫眾生。皮囊盛頭不得
<lb n="0451a20"/>所見。故獲斯罪</p>
<lb n="0451a21"/><p>第五復有眾生。<note n="0451010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謇＝蹇【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謇＝蹇【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451010"><lem>謇</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">蹇</rdg></app>吃瘖&CB00484;口不能言。若有所
<lb n="0451a22"/>說閉目舉手乃不言了。何罪所致。佛言。以前
<lb n="0451a23"/>世時坐誹謗三尊輕毀聖道。論他好醜求人
<lb n="0451a24"/>長短。強誣良善憎嫉賢人。故獲斯罪</p>
<lb n="0451a25"/><p>第六復有眾生。腹大<note n="0451011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">頸＝項【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頸＝項【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451011"><lem>頸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">項</rdg></app>細不能下食。若有所
<lb n="0451a26"/>食變<note n="0451012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">為＝成【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為＝成【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451012"><lem>為</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">成</rdg></app>膿血。何罪所致。佛言。以前世時偷
<lb n="0451a27"/>盜僧食。或為大會福食屏處偷噉。&CB00385;惜己物
<lb n="0451a28"/>但貪他財<note n="0451013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（心）＋常【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（心）＋常【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451013"><lem>常</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">心常</rdg></app>行惡<note n="0451014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔心〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔心〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451014"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>與人毒藥氣息不通。
<lb n="0451a29"/>故獲斯罪</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0724.0451b" n="0451b"/>
<lb n="0451b01"/><p>第七復有眾生。常為獄卒<note n="0451015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">熱燒＝燒熱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">熱燒＝燒熱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451015"><lem>熱燒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">燒熱</rdg></app>。鐵釘釘<note n="0451016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人＝入【明】</note><app n="0451016"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">入</rdg></app>
<lb n="0451b02"/>百節骨頭。釘之已訖自然火生。焚燒<note n="0451017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">身體＝其身【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">身體＝其身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451017"><lem>身體</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">其身</rdg></app>悉
<lb n="0451b03"/>皆焦爛。何罪所致。佛言。以前世時坐為針灸
<lb n="0451b04"/>醫師。針人身體不能差病。<note n="0451018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誑他取財徒＝枉取他物使【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誑他取財徒＝枉取他物使【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451018"><lem>誑他取財徒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">枉取他物使</rdg></app>受苦
<lb n="0451b05"/>痛。令他苦惱故獲斯罪</p>
<lb n="0451b06"/><p>第八復有眾生。常在鑊湯中為牛頭阿傍。以
<lb n="0451b07"/>三股鐵叉。<note n="0451019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔叉人〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔叉人〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451019"><lem>叉人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>內著鑊<note n="0451020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔湯〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔湯〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451020"><lem>湯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>中煮之令爛還
<lb n="0451b08"/>復吹活而復煮之。何罪所致。佛言。以前世時
<lb n="0451b09"/>信邪倒見祠祀鬼神。屠殺眾生湯灌<note n="0451021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">搣＝滅【宮】＊</note><app n="0451021"><lem>搣</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">滅</rdg></app>毛。鑊
<lb n="0451b10"/>湯<note n="0451022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">煎煮＝煮之【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">煎煮＝煮之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451022"><lem>煎煮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">煮之</rdg></app>。不可限量故獲斯罪</p>
<lb n="0451b11"/><p>第九復有眾生。常在火城中煻煨齊心四門
<lb n="0451b12"/>俱開。若欲趣向門即<note n="0451023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">閉之＝自閉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">閉之＝自閉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451023"><lem>閉之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">自閉</rdg></app>。東西馳走不能自
<lb n="0451b13"/>免為火燒盡。何罪所致。佛言。以前世時坐焚
<lb n="0451b14"/>燒山澤。火<note n="0451024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">煨＝燒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">煨＝燒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451024"><lem>煨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">燒</rdg></app>雞子。燒他村陌。燒<note n="0451025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">煮＝諸【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">煮＝諸【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451025"><lem>煮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">諸</rdg></app>眾生身
<lb n="0451b15"/>爛皮剝。故獲斯罪</p>
<lb n="0451b16"/><p>第十復有眾生。常在雪山中<note n="0451026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（為）＋寒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（為）＋寒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451026"><lem>寒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">為寒</rdg></app>風所吹皮肉
<lb n="0451b17"/>剝裂。求死不得。何罪所致。佛言。以前世時。
<lb n="0451b18"/>坐橫道作賊剝脫人衣。使冬月之日令他凍
<lb n="0451b19"/>死。<note n="0451027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生&CB00315;牛羊＝或復生剝牛羊皮【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生&CB00315;牛羊＝或復生剝牛羊皮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451027"><lem>生&CB00315;牛羊</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">或復生剝牛羊皮</rdg></app>痛不可堪。故獲斯罪</p>
<lb n="0451b20"/><p>第十一復有眾生。常在刀山劍樹上。若有所
<lb n="0451b21"/><note n="0451028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">投＝捉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">投＝捉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451028"><lem>投</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">捉</rdg></app>即便割傷<note n="0451029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">支＝枝【宋】【宮】，肢【元】【明】</note><note n="0451029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">支＝枝【宋】【宮】，＝肢【元】【明】</note><app n="0451029"><lem>支</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">枝</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">肢</rdg></app>節斷壞。何罪所致。佛言。以
<lb n="0451b22"/>前世時<note n="0451030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔坐〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔坐〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451030"><lem>坐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>屠殺為業烹害眾生。屠割剝<note n="0451031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">裂＝切【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">裂＝切【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451031"><lem>裂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">切</rdg></app>
<lb n="0451b23"/>骨肉分離。頭&CB00560;星散懸於高格稱量而賣。或
<lb n="0451b24"/>復生懸眾生苦痛難處。故獲斯罪</p>
<lb n="0451b25"/><p>第十二復有眾生。五根不具。何罪所致。佛言。
<lb n="0451b26"/>以前世時坐飛鷹走狗彈射禽獸。或斷其頭
<lb n="0451b27"/>或斷其足。生<app type="＊" source="0451021"><lem>搣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">滅</rdg></app>鳥翼。故獲斯罪</p>
<lb n="0451b28"/><p>第十三復有眾生。攣躄背僂腰髖不<note n="0451032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遂＝隨【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遂＝隨【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451032"><lem>遂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">隨</rdg></app>。&CB00560;跛
<lb n="0451b29"/>手<note n="0451033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拘＝折【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拘＝折【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451033"><lem>拘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">折</rdg></app>不能操涉。何罪所致。佛言。以前世時
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0724.0451c" n="0451c"/>
<lb n="0451c01"/>坐為人憯剋行道安槍。或安射<note n="0451034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">窠＝弋羅【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">窠＝弋羅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451034"><lem>窠</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">弋羅</rdg></app>施張弶&CB00276;。
<lb n="0451c02"/>陷墜眾生<note n="0451035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔頭破&CB00560;折〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔頭破&CB00560;折〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451035"><lem>頭破&CB00560;折</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>傷損非一。故獲斯罪</p>
<lb n="0451c03"/><p>第十四復有眾生。常為獄卒桎梏其身不得
<lb n="0451c04"/>免脫。何罪所致。佛言。以前世時。坐<note n="0451036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">網捕眾生籠＝抄劫人糧食枷【宮】</note><app n="0451036"><lem>網捕眾
<lb n="0451c05"/>生<note n="0451037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">籠＋（枷鎖）【三】</note><note n="0451037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">籠＋（枷鎖）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0451037"><lem>籠</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">籠枷鎖</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">抄劫人糧食枷</rdg></app>繫而畜<note n="0451038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔飢窮困苦〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔飢窮困苦〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451038"><lem>飢窮困苦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。或為<note n="0451039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宰＝帝【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">宰＝帝【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451039"><lem>宰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">帝</rdg></app>主令長。貪
<lb n="0451c06"/>取<note n="0451040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">財錢＝民錢財【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">財錢＝民錢財【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451040"><lem>財錢</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">民錢財</rdg></app>枉繫良善。怨<note n="0451041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">苦號＝酷呼【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">苦號＝酷呼【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451041"><lem>苦號</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">酷呼</rdg></app>天不得<note n="0451042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">縱＝從【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">縱＝從【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451042"><lem>縱</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">從</rdg></app>意。故
<lb n="0451c07"/>獲斯罪</p>
<lb n="0451c08"/><p>第十五復有眾生。或癲或狂或癡或騃不別
<lb n="0451c09"/>好醜。何罪所致。佛言。以前世時<note n="0451043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坐＋（耽荒嗜酒無有度量）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">坐＋（耽荒嗜酒無有度量）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451043"><lem>坐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">坐耽荒嗜酒無有度量</rdg></app>飲酒醉
<lb n="0451c10"/>亂犯三十六失。後得癡身如似醉人。不識尊
<lb n="0451c11"/>卑<note n="0451044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不別〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔不別〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451044"><lem>不別</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>好醜。<note n="0451045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔八萬…過犯〕六十四字－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔八萬…過犯〕六十四字－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451045" word-count="64"><lem>八萬劫墮沸屎地獄。獄卒斬
<lb n="0451c12"/>剉。求死不得求生不得。五窮六極長夜受苦。
<lb n="0451c13"/>以坐貪酒過。受罪已始得為人癃殘跛蹇。為
<lb n="0451c14"/>人之所憎嫉。行逢接他。橫事常無樂時。以酒
<lb n="0451c15"/>過犯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>故獲斯罪</p>
<lb n="0451c16"/><p>第十六復有眾生。其形甚小陰藏甚大。挽之
<lb n="0451c17"/>身<note n="0451046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">疲＝皮【宮】</note><app n="0451046"><lem>疲</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">皮</rdg></app>皆復進引。行<note n="0451047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">立＝步【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">立＝步【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451047"><lem>立</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">步</rdg></app>坐臥以之為妨。何罪
<lb n="0451c18"/>所致。佛言。以前世時坐治生販賣自譽己物。
<lb n="0451c19"/>毀<note n="0451048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呰他財囂＝辱他物矯【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呰他財囂＝辱他物矯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451048"><lem>呰他財囂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">辱他物矯</rdg></app>升弄&CB00356;<note n="0451049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">躡＝捻【明】</note><app n="0451049"><lem>躡</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">捻</rdg></app>秤前後。<note n="0451050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔欺誑於人〕－【宮】</note><app n="0451050"><lem>欺誑於人</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0451c20"/>故獲斯罪</p>
<lb n="0451c21"/><p>第十七復有眾生。男根不具為黃門身不得
<lb n="0451c22"/><note n="0451051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妻娶＝娶妻【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妻娶＝娶妻【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451051"><lem>妻娶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">娶妻</rdg></app>。何罪所致。佛言。以前世時坐喜犍象
<lb n="0451c23"/>馬牛羊&CB00337;狗不可稱數。令此眾生苦痛難忍
<lb n="0451c24"/>死而復穌。故獲斯罪</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0724.0452a" n="0452a"/>
<lb n="0452a01"/><p>第十八復有眾生。從生至老無有兒子孤立
<lb n="0452a02"/>獨存。何罪所致。佛言。以前世時坐為人暴惡
<lb n="0452a03"/>不信罪福。百鳥產乳之時。齎持瓶器<note n="0452001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">循＝順【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">循＝順【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452001"><lem>循</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">順</rdg></app>大水
<lb n="0452a04"/>渚。求拾鴻鵠鸚鵡鵝<note n="0452002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鴈＝鷹【宮】</note><app n="0452002"><lem>鴈</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">鷹</rdg></app>諸鳥子卵。擔歸煮
<lb n="0452a05"/>噉。諸鳥失子悲鳴叫裂眼中血出。故獲斯罪</p>
<lb n="0452a06"/><p>第十九復有眾生。少小孤寒無有父母兄弟。
<lb n="0452a07"/>為他作使辛苦活命。長大成人橫<note n="0452003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝罹【明】＊</note><note n="0452003" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>羅＝罹【明】＊</note><app n="0452003"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">罹</rdg></app>殃禍。縣
<lb n="0452a08"/>官所縛繫閉牢獄。無人追餉飢窮困苦無所
<lb n="0452a09"/>告及。何罪所致。佛言。以前世時坐喜<note n="0452004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔捕〕－【宮】</note><app n="0452004"><lem>捕</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0452a10"/>拾鵰鷲<note n="0452005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鷹＋（鶴鶁）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鷹＋（鶴鶁）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452005"><lem>鷹</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">鷹鶴鶁</rdg></app>鷂熊羆虎豹枷鎖而畜孤此眾生。
<lb n="0452a11"/>父母兄弟常&M010527;憂念。悲鳴叫裂哀感人心。不
<lb n="0452a12"/>能供<note n="0452006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">養＝食【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">養＝食【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452006"><lem>養</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">食</rdg></app>。常苦飢餓骨立皮連求死不得。故獲
<lb n="0452a13"/>斯罪</p>
<lb n="0452a14"/><p>第二十復有眾生。其形甚醜身體黑如漆。兩
<lb n="0452a15"/><note n="0452007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">目＝耳【三】</note><note n="0452007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">目＝耳【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452007"><lem>目</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">耳</rdg></app>復青。頭頰俱<note n="0452008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02196;＝搥【宮】</note><app n="0452008"><lem>&CB02196;</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">搥</rdg></app><note n="0452009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皰＝胞【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皰＝胞【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452009"><lem>皰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">胞</rdg></app>面平鼻。兩<note n="0452010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">目＝眼【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">目＝眼【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452010"><lem>目</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">眼</rdg></app>黃赤
<lb n="0452a16"/>牙齒&CB00565;缺。口氣腥臭矬短<note n="0452011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">癰＝擁【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">癰＝擁【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452011"><lem>癰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">擁</rdg></app>腫大腹。<note n="0452012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">腰＝凸【三】，胅【宮】</note><note n="0452012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">腰＝凸【宋】【元】【明】，＝胅【宮】</note><app n="0452012"><lem>腰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">凸</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">胅</rdg></app>髖
<lb n="0452a17"/>&CB00560;復繚戾。僂脊<note n="0452013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">匡＝曲【三】</note><note n="0452013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">匡＝曲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452013"><lem>匡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">曲</rdg></app>肋費衣健<note n="0452014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＋（言語失則行步勤貸）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食＋（言語失則行步勤貸）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452014"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">食言語失則行步勤貸</rdg></app>。惡瘡膿血
<lb n="0452a18"/>水腫乾<note n="0452015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">痟＝消【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">痟＝消【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452015"><lem>痟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">消</rdg></app>。疥癩癰疽。種種諸惡集在其身。
<lb n="0452a19"/>雖親附人人不在意。若他作罪橫羅其殃。永
<lb n="0452a20"/>不見佛。永不聞法。永不識僧。何罪所致。佛
<lb n="0452a21"/>言。以前世時坐為子不孝父母。為臣不忠其
<lb n="0452a22"/>君。為君不敬其下。朋友不以其信。鄉黨不以
<lb n="0452a23"/>其齒。朝廷不以其爵。趣為趣作。心意顛倒無
<lb n="0452a24"/>有其度。不信三尊。殺君害師伐國掠民。攻城
<lb n="0452a25"/>破塢偷寨過盜。惡業非一。美己惡人。侵<note n="0452016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陵＝凌【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">陵＝凌【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452016"><lem>陵</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">凌</rdg></app>
<lb n="0452a26"/>孤老誣謗賢<note n="0452017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聖＝善【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聖＝善【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452017"><lem>聖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">善</rdg></app>。輕慢尊長欺誑下賤。一切罪
<lb n="0452a27"/>業<note n="0452018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悉＝皆【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悉＝皆【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452018"><lem>悉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">皆</rdg></app>具犯之。眾惡集報故獲斯罪</p>
<lb n="0452a28"/><p>爾時一切<note n="0452019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔諸〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452019"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>受罪眾生。聞佛作如是說。<note n="0452020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悲&CB00079;＝號泣【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悲&CB00079;＝號泣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452020"><lem>悲
<lb n="0452a29"/>&CB00079;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">號泣</rdg></app>動地淚下如雨而白佛言。唯願世尊。久住
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0724.0452b" n="0452b"/>
<lb n="0452b01"/>說法<note n="0452021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令＝化【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">令＝化【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452021"><lem>令</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">化</rdg></app>我等輩<note n="0452022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">而＝令【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">而＝令【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452022"><lem>而</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">令</rdg></app>得解脫。佛言。若我久住
<lb n="0452b02"/><note n="0452023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">薄德＝德薄【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">薄德＝德薄【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452023"><lem>薄德</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">德薄</rdg></app>之人不種善根。謂我常在不念無常。善
<lb n="0452b03"/>男子。譬如孩兒母常在側不生難遭之想。若
<lb n="0452b04"/>母去者便生渴仰思戀之心。母方還來乃生
<lb n="0452b05"/>歡喜。善男子。我今亦復如是。知諸眾生善惡
<lb n="0452b06"/>業緣受報好醜。故般涅槃。<note n="0452024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">爾＝于【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">爾＝于【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452024"><lem>爾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">于</rdg></app>時世尊。即<note n="0452025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">為此諸受罪眾生＝於罪眾生前【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為此諸受罪眾生＝於罪眾生前【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452025"><lem>為
<lb n="0452b07"/>此諸受罪眾生</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">於罪眾生前</rdg></app>。<note n="0452026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">面＝而【宮】</note><app n="0452026"><lem>面</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">而</rdg></app>說偈言</p>
<lb n="0452b08"/><lg><l>水流不常滿</l><l>火盛不久然</l>
<lb n="0452b09"/><l>日出須臾沒</l><l>月滿已復缺</l>
<lb n="0452b10"/><l>尊榮豪貴者</l><l>無常復過是</l>
<lb n="0452b11"/><l>念當勤精進</l><l>頂禮無上尊</l></lg>
<lb n="0452b12"/><p>爾時世尊說斯偈已。諸受罪眾生白佛言。世
<lb n="0452b13"/>尊。<note n="0452027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">修＝作【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">修＝作【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452027"><lem>修</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">作</rdg></app>何善行得離斯苦。佛言。當勤孝順父
<lb n="0452b14"/>母敬事師長。歸奉三尊。勤行布施持戒忍辱
<lb n="0452b15"/>精進禪定智慧慈悲喜捨。怨親平等同己無
<lb n="0452b16"/>二。不欺孤老不輕下賤。護彼如己。汝等若能
<lb n="0452b17"/>如是修行。則為已得報佛之恩永離眾苦。說
<lb n="0452b18"/>是經已。菩薩摩訶薩即得阿耨多羅三藐三
<lb n="0452b19"/>菩提。聲聞緣覺即得六通三明具八解脫。有
<lb n="0452b20"/>得法眼<note n="0452028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淨＋（者）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">淨＋（者）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452028"><lem>淨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">淨者</rdg></app>。若有眾生得聞是經。不墮三塗八
<lb n="0452b21"/>難之處。地獄休息苦痛安寧。<note n="0452029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔爾時〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔爾時〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452029"><lem>爾時</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>信相菩薩
<lb n="0452b22"/>白佛言。當何名此經。云何奉持。佛告信相菩
<lb n="0452b23"/>薩善男子。此經名為罪業<note n="0452030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">報應＝應報【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0452030"><lem>報應</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">應報</rdg></app>教化地獄經。
<lb n="0452b24"/>當奉持之。廣令流布功德無量。諸<note n="0452031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔天〕－【宮】</note><app n="0452031"><lem>天</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>大眾聞
<lb n="0452b25"/>經歡喜。五體投地作禮奉行</p>
<lb n="0452b26"/><trailer><title><note n="0452032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0452032"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>罪業<app type="＊" source="0450007"><lem>應報</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">報應</rdg></app>教化地獄經</title></trailer><juan fun="close" n="001"></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>